notes.note: Please note that this class can be taken for either 3 or 4 credit hours. All students will take the lecture for 3 credits but those who would like an additional 1 credit hour (so total of 4 credits) will need to sign up for one of the OPTIONAL labs. The labs are limited enrollment and will be on a first come, first serve basis. Again, these labs are optional. Please check with Professor Kan if you should have any questions.
